account.descriptionLink:
Proposal to reduce INGOT emission target by 75%.

INGOT emissions target is currently one per minute.

At full demand, this amounts to ~1,440 INGOT and over 100k COAL burned each day.

It would be beneficial to reduce the rate of INGOT emissions so that the COAL supply can slowly reach the threshold for the next supply halving at 25% (5,250,000 supply).

Costs in COAL & ORE will remain unchanged.

With this reduction INGOT emission target will be 0.25 per minute and 360 per day.
account.name: Reduce INGOT emissions
